divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pictures of the Stars, with the camera set at x145 I didn't see the objects until I down loaded the pictures on the computer, there are three different shots with three different objects. I placed them on my facebook page... I didn't know what they were I did notice that they were not from shaking the camera because all the stars are not blurred. I was in my back yard they were taken in different directions off my back porch where it is the darkest.
Summary: one is a group of circles, a check mark and one is like a cylinder
